reviews.name: Clearblue Fertility Monitor Test Sticks, 30 count
reviews.reviewText: When using the fertility sticks and the fertility monitor, the chances of getting pregnant increase dramatically for most women. I became pregnant within 3 months and my friend was pregnant within 2.
reviews.title: Helped me get pregnant!

reviews.name: Clearblue Fertility Monitor Test Sticks, 30 count
reviews.reviewText: Yes, these sticks are expensive, but they are worth it when you are trying to get pregnant. I got pregnant on the first try with these. I have 20 sticks left over, but I am so glad that I don't have try anymore. Don't walk run, to get these with the fertility monitor, it is worth it when you're ready to have a baby.
reviews.title: Absolutely Great!!!

reviews.name: Clearblue Fertility Monitor Test Sticks, 30 count
reviews.reviewText: This system did wonders for our reproduction efforts! First, I had no idea that I'm on a 25 day cycle. What this means is that I was ovulating 3 days earlier than expected. Second, I'm 38-1/2 years old and don't have to years to spend "waiting". Actually, I expected it to take longer so we ended up getting prego earlier than planned! I highly recommend this system if you're trying to get pregnant. The price may SEEM high, but it took only us 2 months to get pregnant, not to mention the cost savings from a medical standpoint!
reviews.title: Superb! Worth the money!

reviews.name: Clearblue Fertility Monitor Test Sticks, 30 count
reviews.reviewText: If you are anything like me, when you are ready to get pregnant you are ready to be pregnant. There is no guessing when you are ovulating if you use this system. It works great and the sticks can be pretty pricey. This is the cheapest I have found them.
reviews.title: 06 September 2011

reviews.name: Clearblue Fertility Monitor Test Sticks, 30 count
reviews.reviewText: I used the Clearblue system and I found it easy to use and follow. We only used it for one cycle because we got pregnant. I will use it again for my next pregnancy. In the past it has taken us well over a year to conceive our other children. Worth every penny.
reviews.title: 29 April 2013
